Alternate-skyculture asterism data (data/asterisms/chinese.json) is derived
from the Stellarium project's "chinese" skyculture
(https://github.com/Stellarium/stellarium/tree/master/skycultures/chinese),
licensed under Creative Commons Attribution-ShareAlike 4.0 International
(CC-BY-SA 4.0). Original authors: Karrie Berglund (Digitalis Education
Solutions), Sun Shuwei. Source references include Yi Shitong, "Chinese
and Western Contrast Star Chart and Catalogue 1950.0" (Beijing: Science
Press, 1981) and the imperial-era "Complete Studies of Astronomical"
(儀象考成, 1756).

The Western asterism set (data/asterisms/western.json) mirrors the
stick-figure lines from data/constellations.json (Stellarium modern_st,
public domain) and is provided as a selectable skyculture in the same
bundled format as the Chinese set.
